.TH STRACEAUD 1 "March 2026" "straceaud 0.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
straceaud \- parse strace output and summarize filesystem operations
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B straceaud
[\fItrace_file\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B straceaud
is a small command-line tool to parse strace output.

Use it with a saved strace file:

.RS
$ strace -o trace.txt your_program
$ straceaud trace.txt
.RE

Or pipe strace output directly:

.RS
$ strace -f your_program 2>&1 | straceaud
.RE
.SH AUTHOR
Daniel Armesto